  "description": "This individual is a weather-beaten human of middle years, with bronze skin thickened by salt and sun. Brown eyes sit deep beneath a low brow, and black hair is kept in a shortknot to clear the face in hard weather. The hands show permanent rope-burn ridges and widened knuckles, marking a life spent working lines and wheel. A healed notch through one eyebrow and a flattened bridge of the nose give the features the blunt set typical of deck officers.",
